data.description: Beautiful rancher with a walk out basement located in this highly sought-after Indigo Ranch at Stetson Hills neighborhood on a double cul-de-sac.  The exterior has stucco siding, an extended backyard patio and offers breathtaking mountain views that will leave you speechless.  This home has 4 bedrooms, 3 baths, a 2-car garage with a floor plan that offers true main-level living.  The entry flows in the dining room, living room and kitchen with stunning hardwood flooring throughout and carpeted bedrooms.  The master bedroom is complete with an adjoining 5-piece bathroom and walk-in closet.  The second main level bedroom can be used as a convenient home office.  Stainless steel appliances include refrigerator, gas range, microwave, dishwasher and washer and dryer.  The lower-level has a large open room for an entertainment center area as well as 2 additional bedrooms and a storage room that can be finished into a small master suite.  There is also more storage under the finished stairwell.   Step out to the newer and larger composite upper deck and enjoy the picturesque mountain and front range views.  The backyard is beautifully landscaped with a sprinkler system and outdoor space perfect for entertaining with a built-in BBQ, refrigerator and a gas fireplace to enjoy during those wonderful Colorado evenings.   The yard is fenced and has a shed for additional storage.   This home is conveniently located to great schools, walking trails, shopping, restaurants, entertainment and travel corridors.   Low HOA annual dues.
